One of the Twitter user, @novieverest said Bakare is number 16
“Buhari is Moses, and Tunde Bakare is Joshua. As it is, Buhari has taken us to the next level of suffering, Tunde Bakare will cross us over to the permanent site.
Another user, @Vhicck tweets, “Now that Tunde Bakare has finally declared his interest to join the 2023 race, I’m expecting Chris Okotie to do the same so that the list of “Usual Suspects” will be complete.
@Etinosa_sama said, “Pastor Chris Okotie thinking about Tunde Bakare not being too FRESH to be president.
Another user, @scad_official said Tunde Bakare has a good chance of winning the presidential election. “That’s assuming he was contesting against Pastor Chris Okotie for C.A.N. President.
@UcheOkorafor4 tweeted, “I gave up on Tunde Bakare a long time ago. The more he speaks, the more I am justified.
Uche Okorafor in his own reaction on twitter said, “I gave up on Tunde Bakare a long time ago. The more he speaks, the more I am justified.
